G A M E - P L O T
-------------------------------------
As the story unfolds, players will 
encounter the mysterious new Distortion 
World, an area unlike any seen in a Pokemon 
video game before. The Battle Frontier area 
(first introduced in Pokemon Emerald) has 
been added to Sinnoh, containing five new 
Battle Facilities for Trainers to challenge, 
each with its own special rules. Players can 
explore the new Wi-Fi Plaza a virtual Pokemon 
amusement park filled with activities, 
including three new mini-games where up 
to 4 players can compete at once.
